name: HyperNginx
tagline: A nginx fork. Aim to migrate to hyperscan or maybe dpdk.
body:
### Welcome to HyperNginx.
This is a nginx branch aimed to migrate with Intel [DPDK(C)](http://www.dpdk.org/) and [HyperScan(C)](https://github.com/01org/hyperscan). It will be update sooner or later. 

### Road map
Update sometime in the future.

### Authors and Contributors
@goby

### Support or Contact
Ok, send me email whatever you doubt or thought.
